Thumbs.db

# Vendored simulator integration (see backends/simulator/vendor/README.md).
# Everything in there derives from the in-house simulator sources. None of it
# may be published here; it is hand-dropped per machine and the `real` backend
# loads it at runtime. Only the README is tracked.
voice_agent/backends/simulator/vendor/*
!voice_agent/backends/simulator/vendor/README.md
